wikipedia_page.main:
Latalia Bevan (born 26 January 2001) is a Welsh artistic gymnast.
Bevan participated in the 2015 Northern European Gymnastics Championships winning gold medals in the individual all-round, team all-round, balance and floor events.In 2018, she won a silver medal for Wales at the Commonwealth Games in the Women's floor event.
